64
00:03:08,915 --> 00:03:10,642
– Erhm, hrm.

65
00:03:10,742 --> 00:03:14,397
Yeah, well, urh. Ya, I can see that. It’s a kind of a rock.

66
00:03:14,497 --> 00:03:18,424
