86
00:04:24,221 --> 00:04:27,273
quite frankly, vain God.

87
00:04:27,373 --> 00:04:29,836
And quite frankly, I can’t.

88
00:04:29,936 --> 00:04:34,034
So I’m leaving Islam. Good bye!

